Soy wax is a creamy, slow-burning wax that allows a full and long-lasting aroma to fill your room. Unlike paraffin candles, there is no pollution to your home, office, or wherever you plan to burn your candle. A natural and cleaner burn for longer-lasting sassiness.

Thanks For Supporting Small businesses!

⭐ P R O P E R   C A N D L E    U S E ⭐
+ Trim the wick to 1/4 inch before each burn.
+ Always place the candle on a heat-resistant coaster.
+ For the best results and longest burn time, burn the candle FOUR (4) HOURS. This will ensure an even burn and a long-lasting candle.
+ Do not burn the candle when there is less than 1/2 inch of wax left in the bottom of the jar. Why? Hot temperatures make things go BOOM! Think about broken glass, wax everywhere and cleaning it up. Burn the candle in sight, keep away from combustibles and keep away from children -all children no matter if they are 1 or 100.
